#: internal/cli/auth.go:24
msgid ""
"Manage authentication credentials for all AI providers.\n"
"\n"
"OAuth providers (interactive browser/device flow):\n"
"  copilot       GitHub Copilot (device code flow)\n"
"  gemini        Google Gemini CLI (browser OAuth)\n"
"\n"
"Multi-method providers:\n"
"  openai        OpenAI (browser OAuth, device code, or API key)\n"
"\n"
"API key providers (paste your key):\n"
"  google        Google AI Studio (Gemini API key)\n"
"  groq          Groq Cloud\n"
"  opencode      OpenCode Zen API\n"
"  custom-openai Custom OpenAI-compatible endpoint\n"
"\n"
"No auth required:\n"
"  ollama        Local Ollama server\n"
"\n"
"Examples:\n"
"  lokit auth login                         Interactive provider selection\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider copilot      OAuth with GitHub Copilot\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai       Choose OpenAI auth method\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai --headless\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider google       Store Google AI API key\n"
"  lokit auth logout --provider google      Remove Google API key\n"
"  lokit auth logout                        Remove all credentials\n"
"  lokit auth list                          Show all stored credentials"
msgstr ""
"Verwaltet Anmeldedaten für alle KI-Provider.\n"
"\n"
"OAuth-Provider (interaktiver Browser-/Geräte-Flow):\n"
"  copilot       GitHub Copilot (Gerätecode-Flow)\n"
"  gemini        Google Gemini CLI (Browser-OAuth)\n"
"\n"
"Provider mit mehreren Authentifizierungsmethoden:\n"
"  openai        OpenAI (Browser-OAuth, Gerätecode oder API-Schlüssel)\n"
"\n"
"API-Key-Provider (Schlüssel eingeben):\n"
"  google        Google AI Studio (Gemini-API-Schlüssel)\n"
"  groq          Groq Cloud\n"
"  opencode      OpenCode Zen API\n"
"  custom-openai Kompatibler Custom-OpenAI-Endpunkt\n"
"\n"
"Keine Authentifizierung erforderlich:\n"
"  ollama        Lokaler Ollama-Server\n"
"\n"
"Beispiele:\n"
"  lokit auth login                         Interaktive Providerauswahl\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider copilot      OAuth mit GitHub Copilot\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai       OpenAI-Auth-Methode auswählen\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai --headless\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider google       Google-AI-API-Schlüssel speichern\n"
"  lokit auth logout --provider google      Google-API-Schlüssel entfernen\n"
"  lokit auth logout                        Alle Anmeldedaten entfernen\n"
"  lokit auth list                          Alle gespeicherten Anmeldedaten anzeigen"

