msgid ""
"Authenticate with an AI provider using OAuth or API key.\n"
"\n"
"If --provider is not specified, you will be prompted to choose.\n"
"\n"
"OAuth providers:\n"
"  copilot       Device code flow — enter code in browser\n"
"  gemini        Browser-based OAuth — sign in with Google\n"
"  openai        Browser OAuth or device code\n"
"\n"
"API key providers:\n"
"  google        Paste your Google AI Studio API key\n"
"  groq          Paste your Groq API key\n"
"  opencode      Paste your OpenCode API key\n"
"  custom-openai Paste your API key + endpoint URL"
msgstr ""
"Authentifizieren Sie sich bei einem KI-Provider per OAuth oder API-Schlüssel.\n"
"\n"
"Wenn --provider nicht angegeben ist, werden Sie zur Auswahl aufgefordert.\n"
"\n"
"OAuth-Provider:\n"
"  copilot       Gerätecode-Flow — Code im Browser eingeben\n"
"  gemini        Browserbasiertes OAuth — mit Google anmelden\n"
"  openai        Browser-OAuth oder Gerätecode\n"
"\n"
"API-Key-Provider:\n"
"  google        Google AI Studio API-Schlüssel einfügen\n"
"  groq          Groq-API-Schlüssel einfügen\n"
"  opencode      OpenCode-API-Schlüssel einfügen\n"
"  custom-openai API-Schlüssel + Endpunkt-URL einfügen"

